The paper discusses a machine learning approach for item recommendation, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the use of normalized nonnegative models, which is a mathematical optimization technique, falling under the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
